 FY 2027 Guardian Angel funding procures these types of equipment: Technical and Personnel Rescue/Recovery including Maritime, Command & Control, Aerial Insertion, Vehicular, Locator of Personnel,
 SONAR, Mission Planning, Information Management Systems and Mobile Intercom System.

 FY 2027 Special Tactics/Combat Control Equipment funding procures these types of equipment: Aerial Insertion, Maritime Rescue, Technical and Personal Rescue/Recovery, and Ground Mobility systems.

 FY 2027 Items Less Than 5 Million increased in order to procure Next Generation Ejection Seats. Funding procures these types of equipment: Aircrew Laser Eye Protection Equipment, Night Vision Goggles,
 Aircrew Flight Equipment Testers, Parachutes, and Next Generation Ejection Seats. Items Less Than 5 Million also includes Enterprise Select Class II new equipment procurement funds Department of the
 Air Force deployers including Extreme Cold Weather Boots, Arctic Equipment, low signature infrared equipment, conformal body armor, rifle rated helmets, and other Organizational Clothing and Individual
 Equipment driven by Combatant Command Theater requirements.

